<div class="paragraph">
<p>Depending on the configuration of your plugin sets and clients, the Mollie assistant has to be completed more than once. Only this ensures that the {payment-method-name} payment methods are configured correctly and all functions such as event procedures and crons run smoothly in the background.</p>
